00:23:27.070 --> 00:23:28.650
And so I went up there.

00:23:28.650 --> 00:23:30.320
And he turns to me.

00:23:30.320 --> 00:23:32.310
Basically, the first thing he
says when he gets into the

00:23:32.310 --> 00:23:36.260
room is, oh, hey, I just googled
Derrick and I love it.

00:23:36.260 --> 00:23:36.890
