graphic design work on floppy

00:23:58.170 --> 00:24:05.570
disks, I swear to God, they
loved the dick joke videos.

00:24:05.570 --> 00:24:06.010
They loved them.

00:24:06.010 --> 00:24:06.890
They thought it was great.

00:24:06.890 --> 00:24:09.670
It was a different thing than
what they were used to, which

00:24:09.670 --> 00:24:12.630
