And it was also a way to let
people know that the DVD was

00:32:36.750 --> 00:32:39.290
coming out and buy it so you can
see your name on the DVD,

00:32:39.290 --> 00:32:40.110
and the movie.

00:32:40.110 --> 00:32:41.540
It's pretty good too.

00:32:41.540 --> 00:32:43.715
It's no your name or anything,
but it's all right.

00:32:46.740 --> 00:32:48.470
So we did that.

00:32:48.470 --> 00:32:52.510
And that battle against weed and
doughnuts has continued to

00:32:52.510 --> 00:32:55.790
be a battle for me, and I think
for a lot of artists.

00:32:55.790 --> 00:32:56.940
And especially now,
where it's like

00:32:56.940 --> 00:32:58.180
people have these computers.

00:32:58.180 --> 00:33:01.190
They don't have to go out and
do anything in particular.

00:33:01.190 --> 00:33:04.420
You're really having to present
a case as to why

00:33:04.420 --> 00:33:09.750
