really from being on the

00:33:30.060 --> 00:33:32.390
street in New York and being
like, we are a thing.

00:33:32.390 --> 00:33:32.860
Come look.

00:33:32.860 --> 00:33:35.830
It's better than just being
wherever you are right now.

