00:33:59.320 --> 00:34:02.220
which is like the least
sexy phrase ever--

00:34:02.220 --> 00:34:06.470
going from a park in the East
Village all the way up to the

00:34:06.470 --> 00:34:07.712
theater, which is on
26th Street and

00:34:07.712 --> 00:34:09.260
