00:34:12.120 --> 00:34:17.540
And you would get a suggestion
at the beginning of the route

00:34:17.540 --> 00:34:20.070
from just a random passerby,
and then you would start

00:34:20.070 --> 00:34:22.080
chanting it, and then
it would morph.

00:34:22.080 --> 00:34:23.400
And as you picked
up more people,

00:34:23.400 --> 00:34:25.110
this chant would morph.

00:34:25.110 --> 00:34:27.920
At one point along the route,
it was just us, different

00:34:27.920 --> 00:34:32.280
sections of the mob, chanting,
Bob Dylan, Jakob Dylan, Bob

00:34:32.280 --> 00:34:35.040
Dylan, Jakob Dylan!

